with a foreign leader.

20:06.800 --> 20:11.467 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
At issue, the Obama
administration's agreement
to resettle refugees not
allowed into Australia.

20:13.033 --> 20:15.067 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
DONALD TRUMP: I love
Australia as a country.

20:15.067 --> 20:19.233 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But we had a problem where,
for whatever reason, President
Obama said that they were going

20:21.933 --> 20:26.933 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
