1,000 illegal immigrants
who were in prisons.

20:28.767 --> 20:29.767 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
And I said, why?

20:29.767 --> 20:31.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Why are we doing this?

20:31.333 --> 20:33.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Prime
Minister Turnbull played
down the incident.

20:33.633 --> 20:37.767 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MALCOLM TURNBULL, Australian
Prime Minister: The fact that
we received the assurance that

20:37.767 --> 20:42.767 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
we did, the fact that it was
confirmed, the very extensive
engagement we have with the

20:44.267 --> 20:48.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
new administration underlines
the closeness of the alliance.

20:48.033 --> 20:53.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Separately, the
Associated Press reports Mr.
Trump told Mexico's president

20:55.133 --> 20:58.433 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
