to deal with -- quote - -
"bad hombres down there."

20:59.667 --> 21:02.667 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
The White House says the
remark was lighthearted.

21:02.667 --> 21:04.533 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Mexico denies it happened.

21:04.533 --> 21:05.533 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
The president's take?

21:05.533 --> 21:06.867 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: I fix things.

21:06.867 --> 21:09.267 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
We're going to
straighten it out.

21:09.267 --> 21:14.267 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Believe me, when you hear
about tough phone calls I'm
having, don't worry about it.

21:16.233 --> 21:19.467 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: All this as the
newly minted secretary of state
tried to rally a work force,

21:21.533 --> 21:25.267 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
many of whom are already
unhappy, following last
weekend's unveiling of
extensive restrictions

21:27.100 --> 21:30.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
for travelers from seven
majority-Muslim nations.

21:30.300 --> 21:32.833 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
