27:15.633 --> 27:17.300 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF:
Reference to NATO?

27:17.300 --> 27:19.333 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JAMES JEFFREY: Exactly.

27:19.333 --> 27:23.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
